OL,3,CHow Andy Burnham's first day as Prime
OL,4,CMinister unfolded
OL,6,FAndy Burnham became Britain's seventh
OL,7,FPrime Minister in 10 years on Monday
OL,8,Fand moved swiftly to settle into the
OL,9,Ftop job.
OL,11,FHis first day began with an official
OL,12,Faudience with the King at Buckingham
OL,13,FPalace before delivering his first
OL,14,Faddress as PM outside No 10.
OL,16,FMr Burnham then moved quickly to
OL,17,Fappoint his new Cabinet.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
