OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1784605665
OL,3,CHow Andy Burnham's first day as Prime
OL,4,CMinister unfolded
OL,6,FThe Makerfield MP, who returned to
OL,7,FParliament in June after a tenure as
OL,8,FMayor of Greater Manchester, was
OL,9,Fofficially elected Leader of the
OL,10,FLabour Party on Friday.
OL,12,FThe formal handover came after Sir
OL,13,FKeir Starmer tendered his resignation,
OL,14,Fwith the King inviting Mr Burnham to
OL,15,Fform a government.
OL,17,F"I now pass the baton to Andy Burnham.
OL,18,FI wish him every success. He has my
OL,19,Ffull support," Sir Keir Starmer said
OL,20,Fin his resignation address.
OL,26,@yD@AOU{D@NO]
