CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1784605665
OL,3,CHow Andy Burnham's first day as Prime
OL,4,CMinister unfolded
OL,6,FBridget Phillipson lost her job as
OL,7,Feducation secretary but was
OL,8,Freappointed as Minister for Women and
OL,9,FEqualities and former deputy prime
OL,10,Fminister Angela Rayner was named
OL,11,FHousing Secretary.
OL,13,FLouise Haigh, a key ally of Mr Burnham
OL,14,Fwho was instrumental in getting him
OL,15,Finto No 10, has been made First
OL,16,FSecretary of State and Chancellor of
OL,17,Fthe Duchy of Lancaster, giving her a
OL,18,Frole as a fixer across government.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
