PN,30308
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1784605665
OL,3,CHow Andy Burnham's first day as Prime
OL,4,CMinister unfolded
OL,6,FFormer health secretary Wes Streeting,
OL,7,Fwho resigned from Sir Keir Starmer's
OL,8,Fgovernment, had been seen as a
OL,9,Fpotential leadership candidate until
OL,10,Fhe backed Mr Burnham.
OL,12,FHe was announced as the new Defence
OL,13,FSecretary on Monday evening.
OL,15,FSeveral senior figures retained their
OL,16,Fpositions, including Transport
OL,17,FSecretary Heidi Alexander and Home
OL,18,FSecretary Shabana Mahmood.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
