FL,304,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30309
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1784605665
OL,3,CHow Andy Burnham's first day as Prime
OL,4,CMinister unfolded
OL,6,FMeanwhile, Labour veteran Pat McFadden
OL,7,Fwill retain his job as the Work and
OL,8,FPensions Secretary.
OL,10,FWithin an hour of his arrival at No
OL,11,F10, Mr Burnham spoke with US President
OL,12,FDonald Trump, who later wished him
OL,13,F"good luck" in a post on Truth Social.
OL,15,FThe US leader added that the new PM
OL,16,F"has got a big job ahead of him, but
OL,17,Fhe will be able to do it" and pledged
OL,18,Fthat the US "will be there to help".
OL,26,@uD@AOUuD@KO]xD@AOUyD@YO]zD@MOUzD@cO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,304,300,200,140,000,100
