OL,3,CHow Andy Burnham's first day as Prime
OL,4,CMinister unfolded
OL,6,FMr Burnham also held calls with
OL,7,Fseveral other high-profile world
OL,8,Fleaders on Monday, including Ukraine's
OL,9,FVolodymyr Zelensky, French President
OL,10,FEmmanuel Macron and Nato secretary
OL,11,Fgeneral Mark Rutte.
OL,13,FEU President Antonio Costa
OL,14,Fcongratulated Mr Burnham on his new
OL,15,Frole in a post on X.
OL,17,F"In the last two years EU-UK relations
OL,18,Fgained a new, positive momentum," he
OL,19,Fsaid.
OL,26,@yD@AOUzD@aO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,304,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30311
