CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1784605665
OL,3,CHow Andy Burnham's first day as Prime
OL,4,CMinister unfolded
OL,6,F"I look forward to continuing to
OL,7,Ffurther deepen our cooperation for the
OL,8,Fbenefit of our citizens and
OL,9,Fbusinesses. The United Kingdom and the
OL,10,FEuropean Union are stronger together."
OL,26,@nD@AOUrD@fO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G11/11
